text: Gord Garvie (25 October 1944 - 6 August 1988) was a Canadian wrestler. He competed in two events at the 1968 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1944 births Category:1988 deaths Category:Canadian male sport wrestlers Category:Olympic wrestlers of Canada Category:Wrestlers at the 1968 Summer Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Saskatoon
